items.title: Air India to deploy A350 services on ultra-long-haul routes
items.description: Following the introduction of the A350-900 aircraft on the Delhi-New York flight, Air India said it will start a five times a-week A350 service from Delhi to Newark’s Liberty International Airport from January 2 next year
